卡迈恩·因凡蒂诺是[[漫画的白银时代|美国漫画白银时代]]的奠基人，其绘制的《[[陈列橱_(漫画)|陈列橱]]》第四期杂志封面，通常被视为正式开启美国漫画白银时代的标志性作品。<ref>{{cite news |author= |url=http://news.comicyu.com/2013/04/07/107867.html |title=漫画巨匠Carmine Infantino去世 |work=[[漫域|漫域]] |language=中文 |date=2013-04-07 |accessdate=2013-04-08 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304191912/http://news.comicyu.com/2013/04/07/107867.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2013年4月4日，于[[纽约|纽约]][[曼哈顿|曼哈顿]]逝世。<ref>{{cite news |author= |url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&id=44738 |title=CARMINE INFANTINO PASSES AWAY AT AGE 87 |work=comicbookresources.com |language=en |date=2013-04-04 |accessdate=2013-04-06 |archive-date=2013-07-02 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6HnkOexhS?url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author= |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/dc-comics-editor-carmine-infantino-434021 |title=DC Comics Editor Carmine Infantino Dies at 87 |work=[[好莱坞报道|好莱坞报道]] |language=en |date=2013-04-05 |accessdate=2013-04-06 |archive-date=2020-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128032024/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/dc-comics-editor-carmine-infantino-434021 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

